careers  pages  home sign in careers why itron internships  scholarships events locations benefits our values search available careers submitor select job family administrative consulting customer service executive facilities finance general management human resources implementation services information technology intern legal manufacturing marketing product marketing purchasing quality research and development sales select region north america europe middle east  africa latin america asia pacific page content​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ ​​ help us create a more resourceful world at itron we help our customers make the most of what they have our technology connects people devices and insights to better manage energy and water resources all around the world as a global company we have manufacturing sales support and administrative offices in  worldwide locations—do you want to help us make a difference explore current job openings itron is an equal opportunity employer itron will make reasonable accommodation to assist a qualified person with a disability in the job application process if you need assistance and would like to request a special accommodation please contact accessibilityitroncom or at  usa for more information on equal employment opportunity please click here ​​​​​​​​​​​​ tweets by itroncareers copyright   itron inc all rights reserved wwwitroncom faq    terms and conditions    privacy policy    contact us itron  wikipedia itron from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search for the software project see itron project this article has multiple issues please help improve it or discuss these issues on the talk page learn how and when to remove these template messages this article needs additional citations for verification please help improve this article by adding citations to reliable sources unsourced material may be challenged and removed april  learn how and when to remove this template message this articles tone or style may not reflect the encyclopedic tone used on wikipedia see wikipedias guide to writing better articles for suggestions april  learn how and when to remove this template message this article contains content that is written like an advertisement please help improve it by removing promotional content and inappropriate external links and by adding encyclopedic content written from a neutral point of view september  learn how and when to remove this template message a major contributor to this article appears to have a close connection with its subject it may require cleanup to comply with wikipedias content policies particularly neutral point of view please discuss further on the talk page september  learn how and when to remove this template message learn how and when to remove this template message itron inc creating a more resourceful world type public traded as nasdaq itri sp  component industry technology founded  headquarters liberty lake washington united states number of locations  sites in over  countries of which  are manufacturing facilities key people philip mezey president  ceo products itron riva smart meters smart grid data collection analysis software data management water comm modules professional services sensing  control solar monitoring revenue  billion   website wwwitroncom itron is an american technology company that offers products and services on energy and water resource management its headquarters is in liberty lake washington united states its products and services include technology solutions related to smart grid smart gas and smart water that measure and analyze electricity gas and water consumption its products include electricity gas water and thermal energy measurement devices and control technology communications systems software as well as managed and consulting services itron has over  customers in more than  countriescitation needed itron openway electricity smart meter with twoway communications for remote reading in use by dte energy contents  history   acquisitions  utilities  recognition  awards  references  external links history edit itron was founded by a small group of engineers trying to find more efficient ways to read meters in hauser lake idaho in  in  itron experienced global expansion into the asian market and developed new manufacturing plants in france and the uk by  itron consulting teams were created to offer services for energy efficiency programs renewables conservation and demand response itron gained national recognition from the white house in  for its commitment to usbased manufacturing and contributions to a clean energy economy within the same year itron and cisco formed an alliance to deliver internet protocol ip communications to the smart grid market thus changing networking capabilities for utilities itron is a founding member of the smart cities council having joined in  itron is also a partner of microsoft citynext helping with global smart city initiatives after developing itron openway riva adaptive communications technology act itron launched the itron riva developers community for the internet of things for developers interested in developing software applications for the iot space acquisitionsedit   itron acquires smartsynch cellular communications and also acquires cn gasgate technology for enhanced smart gas distribution systems   itron expands global footprint and both gas and water metering products are added to product portfolio itron acquires actaris metering systems  – itron acquires schlumberger electricity metering   itron acquires software solutions for distributed system design field workforce management and energy forecasting   itron acquires uts bringing mv metering software application to its product portfolio   aeg meters are acquired with production sites in italy germany spain  south africa  – itron acquires two german companies heliowatt and danyl   itron acquires a number of metering companies including thorn emi gas metering in the uk and bosco spa in italy  – itron acquires allmess congermania and conteuro rigas in europe as well as two us companies for gas and water meter technology sprague and neptune respectfully utilitiesedit various utilities have worked with itron to deploy smart meters advanced communications technology analytics software and other resource management solutions below are some of the utilities that have worked and partnered with itron for smart meter projects north america centerpoint energy southern california edison bc hydro firstenergy dte energy san diego gas  electric cleveland water sacramento municipal utility district glendale water and power rancho california water district los angeles department of water and power ladwp europe middle east  africa edf energy gaz reseau distribution france grdf yorkshire water italgas malta water services corporation state oil company of azerbaijan socar aguas de valencia linea distribuzione stadtnetze neustadt and stadtwerke garbsen asia pacific  australia powercor citipower pt perusahaan listrik negara pln hong kong water sydney water mitsubishi electric corporation tonga power limited tpl south america iberdrola dominican corporation of state electricity companies namc algeria cpfl energia eletrobras elo sistemas eletrônicos elo recognition  awardsedit  north american frost  sullivan award for smart city company of the year best diversity careers company by diversitycareers magazine greentech media top ten smart grid vendors of  greentech media top ten smart grid vendors in  north america frost  sullivan award for product quality smart technology innovation award  at the smart energy middle east conference top  green companies of washington state in  by seattle business magazine at green washington awards the best quality company award by the south african department of trade and industry dti metering international excellence award  african utility week in cape town  business achievement award for growth by the climate change business journal  north america smart grid monitoring  communications company of the year  by new economy magazine  teradata partner impact award for innovation in the independent software vendor category referencesedit  httpwwwitroncompagesaboutasp  history itron itroncom retrieved    internet of things itroncom retrieved    frost  sullivan recognizes itron with  north american smart city company of the year award financeyahoocom retrieved    readers choice best diversity companies  diversitycareerscom retrieved    who are the top vendors in smart grid greentechmediacom retrieved    who are the top ten vendors in smart grid greentechmediacom retrieved    itron honored by frost  sullivan meteringcom retrieved    itron recognized for smart technology leadership itroncom retrieved    the  green washington awards and the first washington green  httpseattlebusinessmagcom retrieved   external link in publisher help  itron factory wins awards from eei south african government nemaorg retrieved    tron wins metering international excellence award for africa meteringcom retrieved     ccbj business achievement award environmentalbusinessjournalcom retrieved    awards and recognition itroncom retrieved    teradata announces winners for its second annual partner impact awards program prnewswirecom retrieved   this article relies too much on references to primary sources please improve this by adding secondary or tertiary sources september  learn how and when to remove this template message external linksedit itron website itron yahoo finance profile retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleitronoldid categories companies listed on nasdaqcompanies based in washington statetechnology companies of the united statesmeter manufacturershidden categories cs errors external linksarticles needing additional references from april all articles needing additional referenceswikipedia articles needing style editing from april all articles needing style editingarticles 