rates in two operating segments energy and water the energy operating segment includes its global electricity and gas products the water operating segment includes its global water and heat products the company’s communications network platform supports robust and standardsbased internet protocol powerlinecarrier and cellular networks supporting multiple protocols according to its customers needs around the world itron sold its distribution design business to geospatial innovations inc itron incitron incorporated on december   is a technology company the company is the global suppliers of a broad range of standard advanced and smart meters and meter communication systems including networks and communication modules software and services the… moreitron incitron incorporated on december   is a technology company the company is the global suppliers of a broad range of standard advanced and smart meters and meter communication systems including networks and communication modules software and services the company operates in two operating segments energy and water the energy operating segment includes its global electricity and gas products the water operating segment includes its global water and heat products the company’s communications network platform supports robust and standardsbased internet protocol powerlinecarrier and cellular networks supporting multiple protocols according to its customers needs around the world itron inc’s information technology department supports business objectives that include providing a wide range of utility software solutions internal it services provide daytoday technology needs of employees the it department is composed of several smaller units the units make up it operations and include human resources information systems enterprise applications software development and business solutions it staff members rely on siebel crm and peoplesoft hrms applications  the department liaises with an it director who is involved with product development and is responsible for security testing and it quality for the companys software solutions  the it department has been involved in ongoing server consolidation using vmware and has expanded use of this technology to virtual machines within the company  sector industry services business services employees  revenue b fye  breaking news on investment signals date type inside scoop  management change company itron inc liberty lake wa change joan hooper senior vice president and chief financial officer cfo itron names joan hooper chief financial officer  project scoop topic software company itron inc liberty lake wa opportunity is focusing on designing implementing and testing new systems in the areas of finance human resources manufacturing and marketing wa spokane   project scoop topic applications company itron inc liberty lake wa opportunity is focusing on designing and programming applications using c programming and visual studio  sc west union  want full access to this profile and more rainkings clients have access to over  new investment signals published daily which provide insights on spending initiatives pain points management changes and more from companies around the globe interested in becoming a client request a demo request a quote technologies currently being used it marketing data analytics databases big datanosql alteryxhadoophp vertica analytic databasemaprnosql databaseserengeti business intelligence cordaibm spssinformaticamicrosoft ssasms sql reporting services ssrsoracle bi eeoracle bi publisheroracle business intelligence enterprise editionqlik formerly known as qliktechsap business objects data modelingmining hyperion essbasesasaccess data infrastructure cloud systems nodejsoracle enterprise managervmware vcloud desktop virtualization vmware workstation email hosting cisco ironport mail server data storage data backup ca arcserveemc snapviewsmartsync disaster recovery enterprise storage emc vnxenetappnetapp storage systemsoracle recove